{"tid":1563220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯表示永遠留巴塞","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:26:33.000Z","uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"de632d6f5551e0b800305429477e416ac61b831c","tid":1563220,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"今季的歐冠盃小組賽，巴塞和多蒙特、國際米蘭、布拉格斯拉維亞分在一起，美斯表示，他希望和巴塞繼續贏得榮譽。「我當然想要獲勝，我想在這傢俱樂部贏得榮譽。這裡是我的家，我不想去其他任何地方，但我想繼續獲勝和具有競爭力。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我能說的是，我想在巴塞隆拿儘可能長久的效力下去，我想整個職業生涯都在這裡踢球，因為這裡是我的家。」"},{"pid":"b6effacf2e820296dbeb2891e4fd49edbc32b6f3","tid":1563220,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"008daf3b9f43f00d60ef3a38fc687359f8be2c89","tid":1563220,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}